title: The Cigar of the Year!
itunes:title: The Cigar of the Year!
description: Today on The Cigar Authority it's the BIG announcement of the 2010 "Cigar of the Year!" Also on today's show Mr Jonathon takes a stab at hosting, "This Date in History," and Tim Pierce from FitTrue.com stops by to check in on Dave's progress in getting back in shape. Did we mention the 2010 Cigar of the Year?!?! It's time for the finer things in life... It's time for The Cigar Authority!
